37
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:50,080
all my life is asleep just a floor below me??

38
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:52,080
It feels strange.

39
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:53,640
Then you should've come to my place.

40
00:05:57,360 --> 00:06:01,480
By the way, how did you know I was here?

41
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,080
Didn't you know?

42
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:05,520
I planted a GPS tracking device on your body.

43
00:06:11,200 --> 00:06:18,080
Have I ever told you about my parents - my adopted parents?

44
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:19,200
I haven't, have I?

45
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:23,120
They were good people.

46
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:29,120
They adopted a 7-year-old boy and raised him so he lacked nothing.

47
00:06:30,280 --> 00:06:33,080
My parents said to me once,

48
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:37,160
"The reason your mother gave birth to you

49
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:39,160
