153
00:14:21,640 --> 00:14:23,920
But for some strange reason, I felt an attraction.

154
00:14:23,920 --> 00:14:25,600
The more I got to know you, the more comfortable

155
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:28,360
it became to be around you, and I wanted to get closer to you.

156
00:14:30,760 --> 00:14:32,600
I seemed like fate that we both like Lee Sol's art

157
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:36,000
and that we live on adjacent floors.

158
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:42,480
It turns out I was right,

159
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:45,120
Brother.

160
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:53,720
Mr. Cha Si-an.

161
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:57,360
