251
00:22:16,480 --> 00:22:17,680
I'm sorry.

252
00:22:20,440 --> 00:22:22,080
Why did you abandon me?

253
00:22:23,480 --> 00:22:25,040
I didn't abandon you.

254
00:22:26,320 --> 00:22:29,880
I thought??I thought it wouldn't take that long.

255
00:22:31,040 --> 00:22:33,880
I was going to go back to you soon,

256
00:22:33,880 --> 00:22:37,040
but who knew 26 years would pass like this?

257
00:22:41,040 --> 00:22:42,160
That day??

258
00:22:45,320 --> 00:22:48,320
I shouldn't have gone there, that day.

259
00:22:49,800 --> 00:22:53,440
I was a a struggling artist and when I suddenly got an offer,

260
00:22:54,280 --> 00:22:57,080
I thought to myself, "Once I get the money,

261
00:22:57,080 --> 00:23:00,280
I'll take Yun-je out somewhere nice tomorrow,

262
00:23:00,280 --> 00:23:02,120
and also take him to the theme park that

263
00:23:02,120 --> 00:23:05,000
he's always talking  about."

